Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.72,0:00:38.62,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Love is magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.62,0:00:39.82,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Attack the mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.82,0:00:41.95,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}On Saturday nights at six, click on Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.95,0:00:43.99,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Today's Conan's 15th anniversary!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.99,0:00:46.03,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Let's solve the monster movie mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.03,0:00:47.79,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.79,0:00:49.63,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.63,0:00:52.10,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.78,0:02:49.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.15,0:02:52.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.38,0:02:53.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.79,0:02:57.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the real Gomera!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.72,0:02:59.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He truly is incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.46,0:03:01.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He looks so strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.39,0:03:03.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been a while, Agasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.20,0:03:04.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mikami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.90,0:03:08.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are these the ones who wanted to watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.07,0:03:09.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.07,0:03:10.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's he?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.88,0:03:16.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Director Mikami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r},\Nmy friend and creator of Gomera!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.17,0:03:19.84,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Movie Director\NDaisuke Mikami
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.91,0:03:19.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet ya, kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.68,0:03:24.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, would you like to\Nsee Gomera close up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.42,0:03:25.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can we?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.38,0:03:29.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's break time for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.19,0:03:30.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.39,0:03:35.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These buildings are tiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.76,0:03:38.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.27,0:03:43.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gomera's back is open!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.60,0:03:48.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A person was born from Gomera!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.14,0:03:51.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's just a suit.\NThey film it to make it look like
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.48,0:03:55.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the monster is rampaging\Nthroughout this miniature city.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.41,0:03:58.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These buildings sure are well-made...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.62,0:04:00.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keep your filthy hands off, you brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.88,0:04:04.59,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Artist\NRyōta Adachi
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.62,0:04:04.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wreck the set and you'll pay dearly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.72,0:04:09.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Director! Do something\Nabout these kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.13,0:04:10.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.73,0:04:13.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Want me to watch them for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.13,0:04:16.00,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Gomera Actor\NShūgo Matsui
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.80,0:04:16.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't have any scenes until this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.80,0:04:18.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I appreciate it, Matsui{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.40,0:04:20.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's a nice guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.04,0:04:22.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gomera is on kids' sides!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.51,0:04:27.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gomera always rampages because\Nof bad adults, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.31,0:04:33.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it's Emera the fairy who quiets Gomera's rage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.55,0:04:32.88,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Actress\NTomomi Sakaguchi
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.42,0:04:38.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Emera? The ring fairy who comes\Nout only when there's trouble?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.89,0:04:40.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.56,0:04:43.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right! Emera's this tiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:45.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She looks just like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.36,0:04:48.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But isn't she a little old?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.33,0:04:50.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hush, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.37,0:04:53.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a nice staff you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.27,0:04:55.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. They all love Gomera,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.74,0:04:59.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and they're like a family that's\Nworked with Gomera for 10 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.88,0:05:02.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That will end this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.45,0:05:06.89,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Movie Producer\NOsamu Kamei
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.48,0:05:06.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Monster movies are childish. Their time is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.49,0:05:11.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Worn-out music\Nand tedious direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.16,0:05:13.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Over-expensive sets\Nand special effects.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.86,0:05:17.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The fairy that was 14 when\Nshe debuted is now 24.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.70,0:05:20.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's time to end this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.07,0:05:24.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes. I hear yesterday's\Nrush film is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.97,0:05:27.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go watch it in the screening room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:30.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're not going to watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.31,0:05:35.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. Say, want to grab a bite, Tomomi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?\NThere's still the matter to discuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.91,0:05:38.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.92,0:05:43.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What matter to discuss?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.12,0:05:44.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's about his next movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.96,0:05:47.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He asked me to be the leading\Nrole as a policewoman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.46,0:05:51.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How can he blame people and\Nthen ask something like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.36,0:05:54.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's to complain about?\NAt least you got some work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.93,0:05:58.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're left out in the cold.\NRight, Macchan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:06:03.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, he asked me\Nto be the villain...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.78,0:06:05.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it's just me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.94,0:06:10.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whatever. Let's go check\Nout the majestic Gomera.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.45,0:06:12.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, Matsui{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.\NThe kids are all yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.78,0:06:12.82,Signs,,0,0,0,,Storeroom #1
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.82,0:06:12.85,Signs,,0,0,0,,Storeroom #1
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.85,0:06:14.72,Signs,,0,0,0,,Storeroom #1
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.99,0:06:17.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Awesome! There's so many monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.82,0:06:20.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're all the ones that Gomera beat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.69,0:06:21.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.13,0:06:27.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry! I didn't think\Nyou'd be that scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.67,0:06:29.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with that hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.57,0:06:32.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Gomera's hand.\NWe use it in close-up shots.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.50,0:06:36.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's also a remote-controlled face.\NWanna see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.31,0:06:37.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.64,0:06:39.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just a sec while I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.74,0:06:41.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.95,0:06:48.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are Gomera movies really\Ngoing to end? They're so good...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.45,0:06:51.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He did say they cost lots of money...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.62,0:06:54.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must be the food costs!\NGomera {\i1}is{\i0} big!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.36,0:06:56.80,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What a bunch of simpletons...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.76,0:07:01.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Matsui{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.57,0:07:05.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened to your leg?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.27,0:07:06.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Gomera!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.91,0:07:07.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gomera?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.87,0:07:12.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was in here! And he\Nstabbed me with a knife!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.04,0:07:13.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is he now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.65,0:07:15.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He ran out that door!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.28,0:07:18.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait! Kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:23.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.59,0:07:25.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can see the studio...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.16,0:07:26.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? There's someone there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.89,0:07:29.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't he that producer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.27,0:07:35.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Matsui{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.67,0:07:41.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.59,0:07:55.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.75,0:07:58.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.69,0:08:01.69,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's no good, he's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.76,0:08:06.13,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Footprints? He must've escaped through that door!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.13,0:08:08.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.47,0:08:12.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.87,0:08:14.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you see Gomera?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.44,0:08:16.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right there. I just ran into him...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.88,0:08:19.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait! Was that Matsui{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.55,0:08:28.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gomera's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.12,0:08:32.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That can't be! There's no\Nplace to hide up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.16,0:08:34.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he flew off?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.39,0:08:36.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}... Gomera can't fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.33,0:08:41.33,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's on the ground?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.33,0:08:42.43,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn it! A suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.74,0:08:50.98,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's empty! That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.11,0:08:56.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pardon my asking, but where\Nwere you at around 11:30 a.m.?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.51,0:08:59.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was on the 1st floor of the studio,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.25,0:09:02.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,doing the final\Ncontinuity checks alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.22,0:09:04.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So no one can vouch for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.72,0:09:05.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.22,0:09:08.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're really sweating a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.99,0:09:11.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I tend to sweat quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.26,0:09:14.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you entered this storeroom,\Nthe killer was in here,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:18.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,already in the Gomera costume?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.30,0:09:19.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.84,0:09:22.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is he all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.54,0:09:27.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I gave him emergency treatment,\Nbut he needs to get to a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.88,0:09:31.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He couldn't have killed\Nhim with that leg...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.25,0:09:35.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the incident occurred,\Nwhy where you here, Sakaguchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.15,0:09:41.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted Producer Kamei to see\Nthe rush of the final Gomera movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.09,0:09:43.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was really well done, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.23,0:09:44.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rush?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.40,0:09:48.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unedited film that was just recorded.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.10,0:09:51.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To think something\Nlike this would happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.14,0:09:56.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, Tomomi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}. You saw the back\Nof the person in the suit, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.57,0:10:01.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, but I'm not sure who it\Nwas. But the way they ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.05,0:10:02.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The way they ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.55,0:10:04.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. They had a hard time running.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.68,0:10:07.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like they weren't used to wearing it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.39,0:10:11.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But of course. That would be the case\Nfor everyone but Matsui{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.39,0:10:15.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words... Matsui{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, Sakaguchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and Mikami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.46,0:10:18.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Other than you three, everybody was in the screening room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.63,0:10:21.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right. I watched the rush too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.27,0:10:24.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's the only one that left.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.94,0:10:28.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, there was\Nanother who snuck out...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.41,0:10:30.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who was it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.01,0:10:31.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.58,0:10:34.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you, I don't know\Nhow this paint got here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.91,0:10:36.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.51,0:10:38.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I snuck out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.75,0:10:43.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I noticed something on the\Nset when I saw the rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.05,0:10:45.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you suspect me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.96,0:10:49.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Adachi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} only snuck\Nout for 4 or 5 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.79,0:10:52.86,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Four to five minutes? That's not enough time to don the suit, kill someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.86,0:10:56.73,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and return to the screening room after running up the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.37,0:11:01.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who put this paint here anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.47,0:11:04.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You did.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.54,0:11:10.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you remember? You left\Nit after the morning rehearsal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.69,0:11:16.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah! I completely forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.75,0:11:17.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.56,0:11:21.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, why didn't\NMatsui{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} watch the rush?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.33,0:11:25.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't ask me. All he said was\Nthat he didn't wanna watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.23,0:11:30.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't say that. He's one of\Nthe ones who wanted to quit Gomera...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.67,0:11:32.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Matsui{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.17,0:11:37.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. I hear he often\Nvented to the producer
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.01,0:11:41.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,about being sick of Gomera and\Nwanting to do normal roles.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.75,0:11:47.75,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I don't get it. Where could the killer have disappeared to?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.75,0:11:51.06,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We followed the footsteps around\Nthe corner and up the stairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.06,0:11:54.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.\NLet's make a grave for Gomera.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.86,0:11:58.10,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And then through that\Ndoor to the roof...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.10,0:12:00.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}! His grave!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.93,0:12:03.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up! This ain't the time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.77,0:12:06.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be getting mad like Gomera!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.67,0:12:08.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like Gomera?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.54,0:12:12.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at this! There's no\Ntail mark on the steps!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.71,0:12:16.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's proof that Gomera\Nwent up the steps angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.01,0:12:19.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because his tail sticks\Nup when he gets mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.22,0:12:21.52,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hold on! Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.95,0:12:24.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.02,0:12:26.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the deal, Conan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.82,0:12:28.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.70,0:12:33.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.97,0:12:34.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.73,0:12:36.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.74,0:12:40.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.57,0:12:42.77,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}All right! I figured out the trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.77,0:12:44.24,Signs,,0,0,0,,Studio A
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.38,0:12:47.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why won't you let us in the studio?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.35,0:12:50.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is no place for kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.25,0:12:52.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.32,0:12:56.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yikes, there's one here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.25,0:12:57.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.03,0:13:05.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.06,0:13:06.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We forgot something!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:06.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.77,0:13:11.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you all doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.64,0:13:12.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.87,0:13:16.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're about to take\NMatsui{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.14,0:13:20.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like he won't be able\Nto play Gomera with that leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.68,0:13:24.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forget Gomera, he can't\Neven play a person...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.82,0:13:28.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So? Have you solved the case?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.99,0:13:31.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I still don't know who did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.59,0:13:36.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did the killer attack\NMatsui{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} in this storeroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.56,0:13:43.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe the killer came to get the knife\Nbut was spotted by Matsui{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.03,0:13:47.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Movie props can't kill people...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.31,0:13:55.51,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Wait a minute! In that case,\Nonly one person can be the killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.39,0:14:05.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector. We're going to take\NMatsui{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.02,0:14:06.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.33,0:14:09.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.36,0:14:14.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one responsible\Nis in this very room!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.57,0:14:16.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.57,0:14:20.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Just move your\Nlips to what I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.37,0:14:23.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on! Let me\Nhave some glory too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.57,0:14:28.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, Agasa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}. If you know\Nwho did it, then please explain
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.85,0:14:31.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,how the killer\Ndisappeared from the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.58,0:14:33.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Special effects!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.78,0:14:36.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know those holographs?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.85,0:14:41.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet the killer was one\Nof them the whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.29,0:14:43.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.03,0:14:48.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?! I ran into the killer in\Nthe hall, and even saw them escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.37,0:14:51.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh, forget what I said!\NThe truth is—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.74,0:14:53.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:55.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An extremely simple one, at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.97,0:14:59.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tomomi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and the children\Nonly saw the killer
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.18,0:15:01.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,until he or she turned the corner!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.41,0:15:05.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no telling if the killer\Nwent up the stairs or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.32,0:15:08.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there were footprints\Non the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.89,0:15:10.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.66,0:15:13.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Follow my voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.46,0:15:14.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.13,0:15:21.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The killer placed the footprints\Non the stairs in advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.07,0:15:23.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hardly anyone goes onto the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.73,0:15:28.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't be strange for\Neveryone to overlook that stairway!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.37,0:15:33.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gomera's legs were probably the\Nonly parts used to make them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.24,0:15:38.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As proof of this, there is a tail mark\Nin the hall but not on the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.18,0:15:43.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The killer quickly removed the\Nsuit in front of the stairs,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.25,0:15:47.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,went down in the opposite\Ndirection, entered a room,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.22,0:15:51.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,lit the suit on fire, and\Ndropped it to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.70,0:15:53.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.66,0:15:55.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.57,0:15:58.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But would they be able to\Nmake the footprints in advance
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.84,0:16:04.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,without knowing the color the\Npaint on the set would be?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.28,0:16:04.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Adachi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:10.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I just happened to put that\Npaint there before the incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.11,0:16:13.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, now, that doesn't hold up...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.78,0:16:16.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's only natural it doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.15,0:16:22.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because Tomomi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and Adachi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nare lying to cover for the killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.59,0:16:24.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.46,0:16:29.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That paint was placed\Nthere by the killer...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.57,0:16:32.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...to use for the footprint trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.20,0:16:35.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So these two know who the killer is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.27,0:16:39.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Adachi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} probably only\Nfollowed Tomomi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s lead,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.58,0:16:42.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but she should know!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.01,0:16:45.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She probably saw the killer when\Nshe bumped into him in the hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.72,0:16:48.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So who exactly {\i1}is{\i0} the killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.65,0:16:52.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The killer was among the four\Nwho weren't in the screening room
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.86,0:16:58.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,or who left the screening\Nroom at some point.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.40,0:17:02.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Adachi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was only gone for\N4 or 5 minutes. Not enough time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.53,0:17:06.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tomomi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} saw the killer with\Nthe children; she's innocent too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.40,0:17:09.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That leaves Director\NMikami and Matsui{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.57,0:17:12.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey now, Matsui{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is seriously injured,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.68,0:17:16.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and Mikami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} is my best friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.41,0:17:18.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And therefore this comes as a shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.72,0:17:20.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes! The killer is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.95,0:17:24.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you doing, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.92,0:17:27.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're bothering me! Shoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.53,0:17:29.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bothering you? Shoo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.59,0:17:33.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, just a noisy fly! Shoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.20,0:17:36.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, who is the killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.54,0:17:42.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The killer is you, Matsui{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.17,0:17:48.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get real! He couldn't escape\Nin that suit with his injury!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.21,0:17:52.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Assuming he really acquired\Nthat injury before the murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.52,0:17:54.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're saying his injury was—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.95,0:17:58.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. After the murder,\Nhe dropped the suit,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.76,0:18:02.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,returned to the storeroom, and stabbed\Nhimself with another knife
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.79,0:18:05.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to deceive us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.30,0:18:09.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the children saw his\Ninjury before the murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.73,0:18:12.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was probably fake blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.00,0:18:15.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This {\i1}is{\i0} a movie set;\Nit would be easy to come by.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.37,0:18:21.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But after they saw his injury, they\Nfollowed Gomera out to the studio!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.41,0:18:25.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's only one way to the\Nstudio from the storeroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.18,0:18:28.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where exactly did Matsui{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Npass ahead of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.69,0:18:38.16,Signs,,0,0,0,,Murder Scene - Studio
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.05,0:18:33.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The studio is right next\Nto the hallway door.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.72,0:18:38.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He probably entered\Nonce the children left.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.26,0:18:43.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He then donned the suit and\Nmurdered Producer Kamei.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.23,0:18:48.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This trick would need witnesses\Nto follow the paint footprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.37,0:18:54.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. So he chose these children\Nwho couldn't follow as quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.65,0:19:00.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Children are bundles of curiosity;\Ntell them not to go and they'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.08,0:19:04.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The suit was lit on fire to\Ndestroy sweat traces inside it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.56,0:19:07.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What proof is there\Nthat Matsui{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.69,0:19:13.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The knife he used to stab himself\Nis in the storeroom prop box.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.83,0:19:16.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was probably the\Nonly place to hide it;
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.23,0:19:19.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he couldn't walk\Nafter stabbing his leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:24.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's one more thing-\Nthe shirt he's wearing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.94,0:19:26.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His shirt?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.14,0:19:30.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The killer ran off at full\Nspeed with the suit still on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.31,0:19:33.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The shirt would naturally\Nbe soaked with sweat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.58,0:19:36.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But his shirt has no sweat stains...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.59,0:19:40.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course not.\NBecause he changed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.06,0:19:42.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He changed it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.26,0:19:45.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This kid can prove this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.16,0:19:47.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can, I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.87,0:19:54.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remember when Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}\Nspilled juice on your shirt?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.81,0:19:57.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that's weird.\NThere's no stain here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.78,0:19:59.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where did you change clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.24,0:20:02.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought you couldn't move\Nwith your stabbed leg?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.01,0:20:06.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you're not\Nmistaken, little boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.08,0:20:09.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe the juice was spilled\Non the floor instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.25,0:20:11.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I really—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.06,0:20:14.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you really sure?\NTry hard to remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.43,0:20:16.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please! Little boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.56,0:20:21.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's over, Tomomi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.73,0:20:25.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's right. I was really sweaty,\Nso I changed shirts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.84,0:20:29.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The shirt is inside my bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.04,0:20:30.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right! Check it at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.41,0:20:33.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would you kill Producer Kamei?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.68,0:20:36.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't he give you work\Nin his next movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.45,0:20:43.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That had never entered my mind;\NGomera was all I thought about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.09,0:20:47.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But weren't you the one who\Nwanted to quit Gomera the most?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.83,0:20:51.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's something that\NProducer Kamei made up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.56,0:20:56.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought it was strange how everyone\Nencouraged me with sad smiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.73,0:21:01.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I only learned of\Nhis lies two weeks ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.27,0:21:05.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hastily negotiated with him, but\Nhe said there was no turning back
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.74,0:21:11.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,as he had already announced\Nthis was the final Gomera movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.58,0:21:18.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone'll have long forgotten\Nthat rubber freak in a year!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.66,0:21:21.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you talk with us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.49,0:21:22.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.89,0:21:28.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was too hard after seeing\Neveryone working hard one last time...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.13,0:21:34.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I regret nothing. Now Gomera\Nwon't have a final death scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.10,0:21:39.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I only feel bad about making\Nthe children see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.35,0:21:46.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, Tomomi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}. Did you really\Nsee him in the suit from behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.92,0:21:52.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't see anything.\NHe disappeared so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.22,0:21:53.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then how...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.82,0:21:58.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I could tell by his movements,\Nwithout having to see inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.36,0:22:05.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, he's been my partner\Nfor these past 10 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.92,0:23:30.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two months later, Gomera\Nmade it onto theater screens.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.82,0:23:35.60,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The last scene was connected\Nwith all the previous films
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.67,0:23:38.46,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and Gomera's death scene was cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.46,0:23:42.17,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Gomera can now live\Nforever on the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.13,0:23:47.19,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Crowds hold their breaths as they\Nwatch the powerful visuals and plot!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.82,0:23:53.21,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yet, Gomera's war cry sounded\Nespecially forlorn to me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.21,0:23:55.71,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}as it echoed throughout the theater...
